<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Yemezler - Make a Reservation</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Coss.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        
        .container.mt-5 {
            margin-top: 6rem !important;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .reservation-card {
            box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            border: none;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: white;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .reservation-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .card-header {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 0 !important;
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            border: none;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .card-header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%);
            z-index: 0;
        }
        
        .card-header h3 {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .card-body {
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        
        .form-control {
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        }
        
        .form-control:focus {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(255,107,53,0.2);
            border-color: var(--primary-color);
            background-color: white;
        }
        
        .form-label {
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
        }
        
        .btn-submit {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            border: none;
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .btn-submit::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 80%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn-submit:hover {
            background-color: #e85a24;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255,107,53,0.3);
        }
        
        .btn-submit:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        
        .policy-card {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            border: none;
            box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
            margin-top: 2rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .policy-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        .policy-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
        }
        
        .policy-header i {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-right: 0.75rem;
        }
        
        .policy-list {
            padding-left: 1.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .policy-list li {
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .policy-list li::before {
            content: "•";
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: bold;
            position: absolute;
            left: -1.2rem;
        }
        
        .input-icon-wrapper {
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .input-icon {
            position: absolute;
            right: 1rem;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            color: #adb5bd;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container.mt-5 {
                margin-top: 5rem !important;
                padding-left: 1rem;
                padding-right: 1rem;
            }
            
            .card-body {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-reservation">
    <%- include('components/header') %>

    <div class="container mt-5 pt-5 mb-5">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 col-sm-12">
                <div class="card reservation-card mb-4">
                    <div class="card-header bg-primary">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt me-2"></i> Rezervasyon Yap</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <form id="reservationForm">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                                    <label for="name" class="form-label">Ad Soyad *</label>
                                    <div class="input-icon-wrapper">
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="Ad Soyad" required>
                                        <i class="fas fa-user input-icon"></i>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                                    <label for="phone" class="form-label">Telefon Numarası *</label>
                                    <div class="input-icon-wrapper">
                                        <input type="tel" class="form-control" id="phone" placeholder="Telefon Numaranız" required>
                                        <i class="fas fa-phone input-icon"></i>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                                    <label for="email" class="form-label">Mail Adresiniz</label>
                                    <div class="input-icon-wrapper">
                                        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="your.email@example.com" required>
                                        <i class="fas fa-envelope input-icon"></i>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                                    <label for="guests" class="form-label">Kişi Sayısı *</label>
                                    <div class="input-icon-wrapper">
                                        <select class="form-control" id="guests" required>
                                            <option value="" disabled selected>Gelecek Kişi Sayısını Seçiniz</option>
                                            <option value="1">1 Kişi</option>
                                            <option value="2">2 Kişi</option>
                                            <option value="3">3 Kişi</option>
                                            <option value="4">4 Kişi</option>
                                            <option value="5">5 Kişi</option>
                                            <option value="6">6 Kişi</option>
                                            <option value="7+">7+ Kişi</option>
                                        </select>
                                        <i class="fas fa-users input-icon"></i>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                                    <label for="date" class="form-label">Rezervasyon Günü</label>
                                    <div class="input-icon-wrapper">
                                        <input type="date" class="form-control" id="date" required>
                                        <i class="far fa-calendar input-icon"></i>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                                    <label for="time" class="form-label">Rezervasyon Saati</label>
                                    <div class="input-icon-wrapper">
                                        <select class="form-control" id="time" required>
                                            <option value="" disabled selected>Saati Seçiniz</option>
                                            <option>12:00</option>
                                            <option>12:30</option>
                                            <option>1:00</option>
                                            <option>1:30</option>
                                            <option>2:00</option>
                                            <option>2:30</option>
                                            <option>6:00</option>
                                            <option>6:30</option>
                                            <option>7:00</option>
                                            <option>7:30</option>
                                            <option>8:00</option>
                                            <option>8:30</option>
                                            <option>9:00</option>
                                        </select>
                                        <i class="far fa-clock input-icon"></i>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <label for="special" class="form-label">Özel İsteğiniz</label>
                                <textarea class="form-control" id="special" rows="3" placeholder="Herhangi bir özel isteğiniz var mı?"></textarea>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-submit">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i>Rezervasyonu Onayla
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="policy-card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="policy-header">
                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                            <h4 class="mb-0">Reservation Kurallarımız</h4>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="policy-list">
                            <li>Rezervasyonlar en az 2 saat önceden yapılmalıdır</li>
                            <li>7 veya daha fazla kişi için lütfen doğrudan bizi arayın</li>
                            <li>Rezervasyonunuz onaylandıktan sonra size bir mail gönderilecektir</li>
                            <li>Lütfen zamanında gelin; masanızı en fazla 30 dakika tutabiliriz</li>
                            <li>İptaller için lütfen rezervasyon saatinden en az 2 saat önce bize bildirin</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('components/footer') %>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-J6qa4849blE2+poT4WnyKhv5vZF5SrPo0iEjwBvKU7imGFAV0wwj1yYfoRSJoZ+n"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-wfSDF2E50Y2D1uUdj0O3uMBJnjuUD4Ih7YwaYd1iqfktj0Uod8GCExl3Og8ifwB6"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Counter-Up/1.0.0/jquery.counterup.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/waypoints/4.0.1/jquery.waypoints.js"></script>
    <script src="/Glass.js"></script>
</body>
</html> 